metadata.name: Scheduler::FollowRecommendationsScheduler #perform when there are no accounts to recommend does not create follow recommendations

sql_query.sql:
SELECT a.attname, format_type(a.atttypid, a.atttypmod),
       pg_get_expr(d.adbin, d.adrelid), a.attnotnull, a.atttypid, a.atttypmod,
       c.collname, col_description(a.attrelid, a.attnum) AS comment,
       a.attidentity AS identity,
       attgenerated as attgenerated
  FROM pg_attribute a
  LEFT JOIN pg_attrdef d ON a.attrelid = d.adrelid AND a.attnum = d.adnum
  LEFT JOIN pg_type t ON a.atttypid = t.oid
  LEFT JOIN pg_collation c ON a.attcollation = c.oid AND a.attcollation <> t.typcollation
 WHERE a.attrelid = '"global_follow_recommendations"'::regclass
   AND a.attnum > 0 AND NOT a.attisdropped
 ORDER BY a.attnum
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "global_follow_recommendations"

SELECT a.attname, format_type(a.atttypid, a.atttypmod),
       pg_get_expr(d.adbin, d.adrelid), a.attnotnull, a.atttypid, a.atttypmod,
       c.collname, col_description(a.attrelid, a.attnum) AS comment,
       a.attidentity AS identity,
       attgenerated as attgenerated
  FROM pg_attribute a
  LEFT JOIN pg_attrdef d ON a.attrelid = d.adrelid AND a.attnum = d.adnum
  LEFT JOIN pg_type t ON a.atttypid = t.oid
  LEFT JOIN pg_collation c ON a.attcollation = c.oid AND a.attcollation <> t.typcollation
 WHERE a.attrelid = '"account_summaries"'::regclass
   AND a.attnum > 0 AND NOT a.attisdropped
 ORDER BY a.attnum
REFRESH MATERIALIZED VIEW "account_summaries";
REFRESH MATERIALIZED VIEW "global_follow_recommendations";
